Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希儿小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见到您呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我洗碗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于堆积如山的工作被我偷懒落下..有事耽搁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果被米娅阿姨训了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以作为处罚..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全是被连累的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 贝尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拜托您啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..干活不必胡思乱想也好啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好凶残的量 我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问..琉小姐曾经是冒险者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 都是过去的事了 有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等级的提升..到底要怎么做才能升级呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不断打倒怪兽就行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 光凭这点还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要获得功绩..具体来说就是击败强大的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真的可以战胜它们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常情况下确实很难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过合理运用战技和策略能够弥补实力的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗的技巧和策略方面 你还有所不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可话说回来 光凭这点依然难以取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般情况下 大家都会采取组队的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的想要变强的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会需要进行组队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便一个人无法战胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此取长补短之后就能击败更强大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生 升级的条件..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 就是“进行冒险”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对每个人来说 冒险的意义都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不清楚你所面对的冒险会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你必须认真面对它所包含的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你想得到的东西 恐怕就位于这条冒险路的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过嘛 我的感觉经常不准就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次 作出反击了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到今天就结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您一周来的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要谢谢你 练得很尽兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 艾丝小姐也..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道能不能追赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拼命追 直到赶上她为止 然后..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 华伦某某的特训真的到今天早上就结束了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 按照计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天开始洛基眷族好像要展开远征
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 结束了吗..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可话说回来 这些能力值..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么上神大人 我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 贝尔 状态..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我回来再看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 贝尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即刻起 我族将挥军远征地下城深层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次为了避开上层的混乱状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也将拆为两股分头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一班由我领头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二班由加雷斯进行指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次行动 赫菲斯托丝的锻造师也将与我们同行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合流地点定于第18阶层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那开始一口气移动到50阶层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目标只有一个 就是未到达区域..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,59阶层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过某些贪得无厌的冒险者打开了“箱子”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍提早了它的登场时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见识一下吧 那孩子的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉..你有没有感觉到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种被人窥视的感觉..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚耶..不过这层给人感觉确实有点异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怪兽数量太少了..冒险者也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天..也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么弥诺陶洛斯会出现在第9层？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我们根本打不过它 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请振作一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..莉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电 火焰闪电 火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说弥诺陶洛斯出现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第9层出现了拿着大剑的弥诺陶洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是那时幸存下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后的一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再未接到过目击弥诺陶洛斯的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 你们几位没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的冒险者呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的房间还有一人被袭击了..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个白发的小鬼 现在大概..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 现在可是远征中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特 缇欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 劳尔 这里能拜托你善后吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时候一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很胆小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话..迟早会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须找机会逃跑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔..贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我也能逃..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放这家伙过去的话莉莉..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是闪避的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光拼速度的话还能扛上一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要闪避掉所有攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕再狼狈 再凄惨..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能争取到时间就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很努力了 现在就由我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得救了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被这个人..用同样的方式..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次又一次..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不奋起挑战的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在畏手畏脚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候才能触及那个高度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到艾丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可以再被艾丝·华伦斯坦拯救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始第一次冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 在地下城抢夺猎物是违反规则的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？那是那时候的番茄小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 那家伙怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像跟弥诺陶洛斯非常有缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说艾丝救下的那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这牛头怪大概是看上了番茄小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以千里迢迢跑来中层找他的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然不肯再被人救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还被对方看到自己再次陷入相同的窘境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出手吗？那孩子才等级1吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会被干掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他啦 缇欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼有男子汉的担当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再被人救 是我的话肯定不想活了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..求求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险者大人 请救救贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你给我放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小人族女孩 你还不能乱动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是帮我们带路就已经很勉强了说..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会报答您的大恩大德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让莉莉做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么都行..所以请救救贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了..救救贝尔大人..贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会 我才懒得救什么小喽啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我更不是那种欺负弱小的小角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪开 艾丝 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是..他不是等级1吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伯特看来那位少年就是个初出茅庐的新手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为英雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像阿格诺一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,640)}Argonaut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.07,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿格诺：古希腊神话中出现的英雄人物，后世称他为冒险家的典范
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是憧憬着英雄的少年的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢那个童话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽..好美丽的景象..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把短刀是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是柄利器 但是不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的闪避真的很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他的攻击却很难奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥诺陶洛斯的肌肉很难砍伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个魔法 不用咏唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 但是对手太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是束手无策了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻冲动..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰闪电！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然赢了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站着昏过去了..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力耗尽..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里维莉亚 那家伙的状态是怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我去偷看么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这个状态不看白不看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么？快点说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全能力S级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔·克朗尼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很努力呢 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上神大人..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..想变强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的..故事的第一页
